{"tid":237580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"願意為新垣結衣離婚嗎？日本男性回覆反映「殘忍現實」","createTime":"2017-05-10T12:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T23:30:24.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f808c779a3732cb576e74adf3c35896c2b2408cc","tid":237580,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"日本女星新垣結衣出道16年來，一直都是許多觀眾心目中的女神，2016年更因主演《月薪嬌妻》，直接被封為「國民老婆」，人氣旺得不得了。近日有網站針對253名男性做調查，主題為「若能與新垣結衣結婚，你願意放棄現在的婚姻嗎」，沒想到透過多重條件調查後，竟反映了殘忍現實。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/1976/d1976437.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1976%2Fd1976437.jpg&h=a7c01d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新垣結衣清新的外型和氣質深受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n日網《sirabee》找來20歲至60歲共253名的已婚男性做調查，其中願意為了新垣結衣而離婚的比例佔全體31.2%，等於每3人中就有1人願意選擇朱千雪子放棄現任妻子。選擇放棄婚姻的男性中，有52.3%是住在東京的居民，且上班族佔了38.3%，顯示無業者為了自尊心還是不敢輕易向女神求婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2512/d2512719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2512%2Fd2512719.jpg&h=fca0109a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲253名日本男性中有3成願意為了新垣結衣離婚。<br />\n<br />\n更值得一提的是，願意離婚的男性中，若以年收入未滿日幣300萬元（約台幣100萬元）當作前提，只有29%敢跟新垣結衣結婚，等於有將近7成的人覺得「口袋不飽就養不起結衣」，調查結果讓不少網友笑說「整體看來還是很現實的」、「離婚還需給前妻贍養費呀」、「白日夢做做就好」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2512/d2512720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2512%2Fd2512720.jpg&h=da623774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有將近7成的男性在年收入未滿300萬元的前提下不敢貿然離婚。"},{"pid":"a008311f33ef212aa6580a01fce8d6baadd087e5","tid":237580,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"朱千雪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b298eceddb6d3c6afbf5dec680070d5f0307fa9","tid":237580,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:59:06.000Z","msg":"妻子人選只有結衣 何來離婚?"},{"pid":"9d1701949a37b86e0050c0f15f7cea16d70af591","tid":237580,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"竟然得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c277e87a39cb641f676e88f0eb239251652579","tid":237580,"uid":7466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朱千雪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01419ef1fb24a60b6810bebfbc61c8fe891a3971","tid":237580,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朱千雪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f49fcd8ebaba0d18cd2636774b4d9409d4158df","tid":237580,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能有d有老婆係隔離呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似香港d街訪都係女朋友面前問個男嘅會唔會偷食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b9dedc15880e1c105cea35dce199011449641e","tid":237580,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f371e42ed4b71a127e9478fa087b6e27f0ef4c","tid":237580,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:45:36.000Z","msg":"等於每3人中就有1人願意選擇朱千雪子放棄現任妻子<br />\n會唔會太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3623a09a429643b0f4b1c61a6f554da1a401bea9","tid":237580,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:12:20.000Z","msg":"又吹奏新坦結衣"},{"pid":"62e1802a0661490864c856b8d3e486104e90e2ac","tid":237580,"uid":89411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"咪又係會老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ea7944fd29a509b57a7778e74e301ecbc46225","tid":237580,"uid":32280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"那個了唷!"},{"pid":"7b30cb16bf531d5f89ea728b40a6f7983d6d790d","tid":237580,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"多謝大家支持我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你地離婚都無用<br />\n我老婆已經有老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b904879361ad8742396b5b4f20f1447b59c9306","tid":237580,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57e8bd45da231ffd6fc877bbbb85c662f0b21687","tid":237580,"uid":14119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"點解要同結衣離婚再同返結衣結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 梗係唔離啦麻鬼煩"},{"pid":"95134cb77cc1a8a55d74e33c756b84992c6db21c","tid":237580,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"離婚夢貼正室講: 我跟新桓那個了唷"},{"pid":"65c9b1ef858ee9e0e328e20c8d3e596039c0d307","tid":237580,"uid":